                     | npm run quality:engine · npm run quality:studio                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |","beforeFullFileContent":"---\n\n# Studio V2.0 · 语音留言改造执行索引（gbx / general-batch-exe）\n\n# 用法：node .cursor/skills/general-batch-exe/bin/gbx.js --exFile <本文件> --workdir <仓库根> [--dry-run]\n\n# 本轮目标：cardKind=voicemail + attach/schedule 分流 + 外置物化端口 + Studio/样例/调试最小闭环\n\nbatch_size: 3\n\nmax_rounds: 80 \n\nmax_fix_attempts: 5 \n\nmax_ineffective_fixes: 2 \n\nstop_on_fail: true \n\ngroup: order\n\nverify_default:\n\n- npm run quality:engine\n\nread_first:\n\n- AGENTS.md\n- .cursor/rules/codingRole.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/engine-code-quality.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/studio-boundaries.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/studio-v2-quality.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/testing-and-quality.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/docs-execution.mdc\n- docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造需求.md\n- docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\n- docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\n- docs/AI和人类/需求/04-调试器界面需求.md\n- docs/AI和人类/需求/08-内容校验规则.md\n- docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md\n- docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/schema/callCard.ts\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/schema/outcome.ts\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/runtime/effectExecutor.ts\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/runtime/effectSink.ts\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/runtime/scheduleTick.ts\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/host/createEngineHost.ts\n- data/storis-packages/wrong_number_act1/cards/lanxing_voicemail.s-card.json\n- data/storis-packages/wrong_number_act1/cards/lanxing_callback_intro.s-card.json\n- apps/studioV2/typeFiles/story/callCardLabels.ts\n- apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/com/panel/ExitListEditor/com/effects/ExitEffectPanel.tsx\n\nhard_stop_patterns:\n\n- \"协议未定|需要人工决策|阻塞实现\"\n- \"create_voicemail 仍作新写真源|Studio 下拉仍保留创建语音信箱\"\n- \"voicemail 写入 Board.pending|schedule(voicemail) 仍 agent_outbound 响铃\"\n- \"在 effectExecutor 内直接调 LLM|隐式扫描 transcript 拼留言\"\n- \"引擎持 LLM Key|rpg-engine 引进 react|编辑 docs/人类/\"\n- \"interactionMode 非 playback_only 的 voicemail 可过 validate\"\n- \"quality:engine 失败仍标完成\"\n- \"留下 @deprecated 已迁至|兼容转发壳当长期方案\"\n\nexecutor_extra: |\n  只实现当前 ACTIVE / 本轮选出的 ⬜ 行；完成后把对应行改为 ✅。\n  需求真源：语音留言改造需求.md。刀序 V2-VM-1 → V2-VM-14；严格 group: order。\n  阶段：A 文档契约(1) → B Schema/校验(2–3) → C 运行时分流+物化(4–7) → D Studio(8–9) → E 样例(10) → F 调试最小(11) → G 文档回写+收口(12–14)。\n  voicemail 永不进 Board.pending；schedule(voicemail)=延迟进信箱。\n  生成与未读通知分端口；引擎外 LLM。\n  废弃 create_voicemail（校验拒绝 + UI 删除）。\n\nreviewer_extra: |\n  只读审查；写出 reviews/latest.json。\n  对照 语音留言改造需求.md §3–§5。\n  blocker：仍进 Board、仍外呼响铃、仍 create_voicemail 新写、物化塞进 Executor、mode 未锁定、engine 红。\n\nfixer_extra: |\n  只修审查与 verify 确认问题；禁止无关重构。\n  引擎任务 quality:engine；触及 Studio 时加 quality:studio。\n  触碰 Studio 历史空格文件整文件改 tab。\n\nworkflow_dir: .ai-workflow-v2-voicemail\nadapter: table\n---\n\n# Studio V2.0 · 语音留言改造执行索引\n\n> **用法：**  \n> `node .cursor/skills/general-batch-exe/bin/gbx.js --exFile docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造_执行索引.md --workdir . --dry-run`  \n> **独立 workflow：** `.ai-workflow-v2-voicemail/`  \n> **需求真源：** [语音留言改造需求.md](./语音留言改造需求.md)\n\n本文回答：**语音留言从 Effect 桩改为** `cardKind=voicemail` **+ 物化管线**按什么顺序做、做到哪算完。\n\n---\n\n\n\n## 0. 已钉死口径\n\n\n\n### 0.1 范围边界\n\n\n| 做                                                          | 不做（本轮）            |\n| ---------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------- |\n| `cardKind=voicemail` + `mailbox_open` + 强制 `playback_only` | 引擎内置 LLM          |\n| attach/schedule 分流；永不进 Board                               | 真机 LED 硬件驱动       |\n| VoicemailMaterialize + 外置生成/未读端口                           | 隐式扫 transcript    |\n| 废弃 `create_voicemail`（引擎+Studio）                           | 完整调试台大改版（仅最小信箱路径） |\n| 样例包迁移                                                      | 第二幕扩写             |\n\n\n\n\n### 0.2 推荐刀序\n\n```text\nV2-VM-1    需求/技术设计回写骨架（01/02 关键口径先落，实现中可微调）\nV2-VM-2    Schema：CardKind/EntryMode；Profile telephony 槽与未读推导\nV2-VM-3    validatePackage：voicemail 强制 mode；拒绝 create_voicemail；单测\nV2-VM-4    effectExecutor：attach(voicemail)→GenStack；lookupCard\nV2-VM-5    scheduleTick：once→voicemail 入栈/物化，禁止 agent_outbound\nV2-VM-6    VoicemailMaterializePipeline + Host 挂接（plan 终态后）\nV2-VM-7    端口：generateVoicemail / onVoicemailUnreadChanged；noop + 单测\nV2-VM-8    Studio：卡种/字段锁定；标签与属性表单\nV2-VM-9    Studio：Effect 下拉删 create_voicemail；attach/schedule 摘要「进信箱」\nV2-VM-10   样例 wrong_number_act1：lanxing_voicemail 改 kind；出口改 attach\nV2-VM-11   调试最小：信箱列表 / 未读 / 模拟听完跑 exits（或 Host 单测等价）\nV2-VM-12   废弃 create_voicemail 全仓清理（Sink/测试/旧面板文件）\nV2-VM-13   需求 04/08 + 技术设计 07/19 收口对齐\nV2-VM-14   验收勾选 + quality:engine（+ studio）绿\n```\n\n`group: order`：严格按表取 ⬜。\n\n> **gbx 表解析注意：** 任务单元格勿写英文 `status`、勿写「状态」子串。\n\n\n\n### 0.3 全批声明\n\n```text\n行为目标：留言=voicemail 卡；挂卡进信箱；外置物化；听完走 exits\nverify：quality:engine（Studio 任务另加 quality:studio）\nmax_rounds：80\n```\n\n---\n\n\n\n## 1. 任务表\n\n\n| 状态  | ID       | 任务                                                                                            | verify                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| --- | -------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-1  | **文档骨架**：按需求 §3 回写需求 01/02 中 CardKind、EntryMode、attach/schedule 分流与废弃 create_voicemail 段落     | test -f \"docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\" && test -f \"docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\" && grep -q 'voicemail' \"docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\" && grep -q 'mailbox_open' \"docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\" && grep -q 'create_voicemail' \"docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\" |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-2  | **Schema**：`voicemail` / `mailbox_open`；telephony 槽字段与未读推导；导出门面                               | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-3  | **校验**：voicemail 强制 playback_only+mailbox_open+deny_all；create_voicemail error；VOICEMAIL_* 单测 | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-4  | **attach 分流**：目标 voicemail → GenStack，不写 Board.pending；负向单测                                   | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-5  | **schedule 分流**：目标 voicemail → 延迟入栈/物化，非 agent_outbound；advanceClock 单测                       | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-6  | **Materialize**：plan 终态后出栈写槽；失败不回滚其它 effect；Host 挂接                                           | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-7  | **端口**：generateVoicemail / onVoicemailUnreadChanged 可注入；noop/recording 单测                     | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-8  | **Studio 卡种**：下拉「语音留言」；interactionMode/entryMode 锁定 disable                                   | npm run quality:studio                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ⬜   | V2-VM-9  | **Studio Effect**：删除 create_voicemail 面板与枚举；attach/schedule 人话标明进信箱                           | npm run quality:studio                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ⬜   | V2-VM-10 | **样例包**：`lanxing_voicemail` 改 cardKind；callback 出口 attach 替代 create_voicemail；validate 绿      | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ⬜   | V2-VM-11 | **调试/听完路径**：信箱最小 UI 或 Host 单测证明 mailbox_open → Outcome → exits                                | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ⬜   | V2-VM-12 | **全仓清理**：Sink/旧测试/旧面板文件去掉 create_voicemail 新写路径                                               | npm run quality:engine · npm run quality:studio                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |\n| ⬜   | V2-VM-13 | **文档收口**：需求 04/08、技术设计 07/19 与实现一致                                                            | test -f \"docs/AI和人类/需求/04-调试器界面需求.md\" && test -f \"docs/AI和人类/需求/08-内容校验规则.md\" && test -f \"docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md\" && test -f \"docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md\"                                                                                         |\n| ⬜   | V2-VM-14 | **验收**：需求 §5 勾选；quality:engine + quality:studio 全绿                                            | npm run quality:engine · npm run quality:studio                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |\n\n\n---\n\n\n\n## 2. 批次出口（每批结束后）\n\n- 本批任务行均为 ✅  \n- verify / verify_default exit 0  \n- Reviewer：blocker=0 且 critical=0\n\n**阶段关注点：**\n\n- **VM-1–3**：契约与校验先于运行时  \n- **VM-4–7**：分流 + 物化 + 端口；禁止进 Board / 禁止 Executor 调 LLM  \n- **VM-8–9**：Studio 与引擎枚举一致  \n- **VM-10**：第一幕样例可 validate  \n- **VM-11–14**：听完出口可证 + 文档与门禁收口\n\n---\n\n\n\n## 3. 本轮总出口（V2-VM-1–14 ✅ 后）\n\n- [ ] Schema / 校验支持 voicemail 强制组合  \n- [ ] attach/schedule(voicemail) 不进 Board；延迟进信箱  \n- [ ] Materialize + 外置端口；未读可通知  \n- [ ] Studio 无 create_voicemail；字段锁定  \n- [ ] wrong_number_act1 已迁移  \n- [ ] 听完 exits 可证（单测或最小调试）  \n- [ ] 需求/技术设计已回写  \n- [ ] quality:engine + quality:studio 绿  \n\n收口后 **不要在本文件继续加任务**；增量另开里程碑。\n\n---\n\n\n\n## 4. 任务 ↔ 需求映射\n\n\n| 任务          | 语音留言改造需求          |\n| ----------- | ----------------- |\n| V2-VM-1     | §3 · §6（01/02 先行） |\n| V2-VM-2–3   | §3.1–§3.2 · §5    |\n| V2-VM-4–5   | §3.3              |\n| V2-VM-6–7   | §3.4–§3.6 · §4    |\n| V2-VM-8–9   | §3.7              |\n| V2-VM-10    | §1.2 · §5 样例      |\n| V2-VM-11    | §3.5 · 需求 04      |\n| V2-VM-12–14 | §5–§6 收口          |\n\n\n---\n\n\n\n## 5. 给执行者的提醒\n\n- **先** `--dry-run` 再正式跑 gbx。  \n- **先校验后分流**：未 VM-3 不要宣称旧包已拒 `create_voicemail`。  \n- **lookupCard 必备**：attach/schedule 分流依赖能解析目标 `cardKind`。  \n- **生成与 LED 分端口**；Profile 为未读真源。  \n- **样例迁移前**保留失败单测对照，避免假绿。  \n- 脏树 checkpoint 会 BLOCKED。  \n- **不要自动 commit**，除非用户明确要求。\n\n","afterFullFileContent":"---\n\n# Studio V2.0 · 语音留言改造执行索引（gbx / general-batch-exe）\n\n# 用法：node .cursor/skills/general-batch-exe/bin/gbx.js --exFile <本文件> --workdir <仓库根> [--dry-run]\n\n# 本轮目标：cardKind=voicemail + attach/schedule 分流 + 外置物化端口 + Studio/样例/调试最小闭环\n\nbatch_size: 3\n\nmax_rounds: 80 \n\nmax_fix_attempts: 5 \n\nmax_ineffective_fixes: 2 \n\nstop_on_fail: true \n\ngroup: order\n\nverify_default:\n\n- npm run quality:engine\n\nread_first:\n\n- AGENTS.md\n- .cursor/rules/codingRole.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/engine-code-quality.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/studio-boundaries.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/studio-v2-quality.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/testing-and-quality.mdc\n- .cursor/rules/docs-execution.mdc\n- docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造需求.md\n- docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\n- docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\n- docs/AI和人类/需求/04-调试器界面需求.md\n- docs/AI和人类/需求/08-内容校验规则.md\n- docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md\n- docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/schema/callCard.ts\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/schema/outcome.ts\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/runtime/effectExecutor.ts\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/runtime/effectSink.ts\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/runtime/scheduleTick.ts\n- packages/rpg-engine/src/host/createEngineHost.ts\n- data/storis-packages/wrong_number_act1/cards/lanxing_voicemail.s-card.json\n- data/storis-packages/wrong_number_act1/cards/lanxing_callback_intro.s-card.json\n- apps/studioV2/typeFiles/story/callCardLabels.ts\n- apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/com/panel/ExitListEditor/com/effects/ExitEffectPanel.tsx\n\nhard_stop_patterns:\n\n- \"协议未定|需要人工决策|阻塞实现\"\n- \"create_voicemail 仍作新写真源|Studio 下拉仍保留创建语音信箱\"\n- \"voicemail 写入 Board.pending|schedule(voicemail) 仍 agent_outbound 响铃\"\n- \"在 effectExecutor 内直接调 LLM|隐式扫描 transcript 拼留言\"\n- \"引擎持 LLM Key|rpg-engine 引进 react|编辑 docs/人类/\"\n- \"interactionMode 非 playback_only 的 voicemail 可过 validate\"\n- \"quality:engine 失败仍标完成\"\n- \"留下 @deprecated 已迁至|兼容转发壳当长期方案\"\n\nexecutor_extra: |\n  只实现当前 ACTIVE / 本轮选出的 ⬜ 行；完成后把对应行改为 ✅。\n  需求真源：语音留言改造需求.md。刀序 V2-VM-1 → V2-VM-14；严格 group: order。\n  阶段：A 文档契约(1) → B Schema/校验(2–3) → C 运行时分流+物化(4–7) → D Studio(8–9) → E 样例(10) → F 调试最小(11) → G 文档回写+收口(12–14)。\n  voicemail 永不进 Board.pending；schedule(voicemail)=延迟进信箱。\n  生成与未读通知分端口；引擎外 LLM。\n  废弃 create_voicemail（校验拒绝 + UI 删除）。\n\nreviewer_extra: |\n  只读审查；写出 reviews/latest.json。\n  对照 语音留言改造需求.md §3–§5。\n  blocker：仍进 Board、仍外呼响铃、仍 create_voicemail 新写、物化塞进 Executor、mode 未锁定、engine 红。\n\nfixer_extra: |\n  只修审查与 verify 确认问题；禁止无关重构。\n  引擎任务 quality:engine；触及 Studio 时加 quality:studio。\n  触碰 Studio 历史空格文件整文件改 tab。\n\nworkflow_dir: .ai-workflow-v2-voicemail\nadapter: table\n---\n\n# Studio V2.0 · 语音留言改造执行索引\n\n> **用法：**  \n> `node .cursor/skills/general-batch-exe/bin/gbx.js --exFile docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造_执行索引.md --workdir . --dry-run`  \n> **独立 workflow：** `.ai-workflow-v2-voicemail/`  \n> **需求真源：** [语音留言改造需求.md](./语音留言改造需求.md)\n\n本文回答：**语音留言从 Effect 桩改为** `cardKind=voicemail` **+ 物化管线**按什么顺序做、做到哪算完。\n\n---\n\n\n\n## 0. 已钉死口径\n\n\n\n### 0.1 范围边界\n\n\n| 做                                                          | 不做（本轮）            |\n| ---------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------- |\n| `cardKind=voicemail` + `mailbox_open` + 强制 `playback_only` | 引擎内置 LLM          |\n| attach/schedule 分流；永不进 Board                               | 真机 LED 硬件驱动       |\n| VoicemailMaterialize + 外置生成/未读端口                           | 隐式扫 transcript    |\n| 废弃 `create_voicemail`（引擎+Studio）                           | 完整调试台大改版（仅最小信箱路径） |\n| 样例包迁移                                                      | 第二幕扩写             |\n\n\n\n\n### 0.2 推荐刀序\n\n```text\nV2-VM-1    需求/技术设计回写骨架（01/02 关键口径先落，实现中可微调）\nV2-VM-2    Schema：CardKind/EntryMode；Profile telephony 槽与未读推导\nV2-VM-3    validatePackage：voicemail 强制 mode；拒绝 create_voicemail；单测\nV2-VM-4    effectExecutor：attach(voicemail)→GenStack；lookupCard\nV2-VM-5    scheduleTick：once→voicemail 入栈/物化，禁止 agent_outbound\nV2-VM-6    VoicemailMaterializePipeline + Host 挂接（plan 终态后）\nV2-VM-7    端口：generateVoicemail / onVoicemailUnreadChanged；noop + 单测\nV2-VM-8    Studio：卡种/字段锁定；标签与属性表单\nV2-VM-9    Studio：Effect 下拉删 create_voicemail；attach/schedule 摘要「进信箱」\nV2-VM-10   样例 wrong_number_act1：lanxing_voicemail 改 kind；出口改 attach\nV2-VM-11   调试最小：信箱列表 / 未读 / 模拟听完跑 exits（或 Host 单测等价）\nV2-VM-12   废弃 create_voicemail 全仓清理（Sink/测试/旧面板文件）\nV2-VM-13   需求 04/08 + 技术设计 07/19 收口对齐\nV2-VM-14   验收勾选 + quality:engine（+ studio）绿\n```\n\n`group: order`：严格按表取 ⬜。\n\n> **gbx 表解析注意：** 任务单元格勿写英文 `status`、勿写「状态」子串。\n\n\n\n### 0.3 全批声明\n\n```text\n行为目标：留言=voicemail 卡；挂卡进信箱；外置物化；听完走 exits\nverify：quality:engine（Studio 任务另加 quality:studio）\nmax_rounds：80\n```\n\n---\n\n\n\n## 1. 任务表\n\n\n| 状态  | ID       | 任务                                                                                            | verify                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| --- | -------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-1  | **文档骨架**：按需求 §3 回写需求 01/02 中 CardKind、EntryMode、attach/schedule 分流与废弃 create_voicemail 段落     | test -f \"docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\" && test -f \"docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\" && grep -q 'voicemail' \"docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\" && grep -q 'mailbox_open' \"docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\" && grep -q 'create_voicemail' \"docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\" |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-2  | **Schema**：`voicemail` / `mailbox_open`；telephony 槽字段与未读推导；导出门面                               | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-3  | **校验**：voicemail 强制 playback_only+mailbox_open+deny_all；create_voicemail error；VOICEMAIL_* 单测 | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-4  | **attach 分流**：目标 voicemail → GenStack，不写 Board.pending；负向单测                                   | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-5  | **schedule 分流**：目标 voicemail → 延迟入栈/物化，非 agent_outbound；advanceClock 单测                       | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-6  | **Materialize**：plan 终态后出栈写槽；失败不回滚其它 effect；Host 挂接                                           | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-7  | **端口**：generateVoicemail / onVoicemailUnreadChanged 可注入；noop/recording 单测                     | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-8  | **Studio 卡种**：下拉「语音留言」；interactionMode/entryMode 锁定 disable                                   | npm run quality:studio                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-9  | **Studio Effect**：删除 create_voicemail 面板与枚举；attach/schedule 人话标明进信箱                           | npm run quality:studio                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-10 | **样例包**：`lanxing_voicemail` 改 cardKind；callback 出口 attach 替代 create_voicemail；validate 绿      | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n| ✅   | V2-VM-11 | **调试/听完路径**：信箱最小 UI 或 Host 单测证明 mailbox_open → Outcome → exits                                | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                   